data.editorText:
intro h,
induction t with t ht,
repeat{rw add_zero at h},
exact h,
repeat{rw add_succ at h},
rw succ_eq_succ_iff (a + t) (b + t) at h,
apply ht,
exact h,

data.lean: lemma eq_zero_of_add_right_eq_self {a b : mynat} : a + b = a → b = 0 :=
data.editorText:
intro h,
rw ← zero_add a at h,
rw add_assoc 0 a b at h,
rw add_comm a b at h,
rw ← add_assoc 0 b a at h,
rw add_right_cancel_iff (a) (0+b) (0) at h,
rw zero_add at h,
exact h,

exfalso,
apply succ_ne_zero (a+b'),

data.lean: lemma ne_succ_self (n : mynat) : n ≠ succ n :=
data.editorText:
intro h,
rw succ_eq_add_one n at h,
rw ← zero_add n at h,
rw add_assoc 0 n 1 at h,
rw add_comm n 1 at h,
rw ← add_assoc 0 1 n at h,
rw zero_add 1 at h,
rw add_right_cancel_iff n 0 1 at h,
contradiction,

data.lean: theorem mul_pos (a b : mynat) : a ≠ 0 → b ≠ 0 → a * b ≠ 0 :=
data.editorText:
intros ha0 hb0 hab,
cases a with a,
  apply ha0,
  refl,
  cases b with b,
    apply hb0,
    refl,
    rw succ_mul at hab,
    rw add_succ at hab,
    exact succ_ne_zero _ hab,

data.lean:
theorem eq_zero_or_eq_zero_of_mul_eq_zero (a b : mynat) (h : a * b = 0) :
  a = 0 ∨ b = 0 :=
data.editorText:
cases a with a,
  left,
  refl,
  cases b with b,
    right,
    refl,
    right,
    exfalso,
    rw succ_mul at h,
    rw add_succ at h,
    exact succ_ne_zero _ h,

data.lean: theorem mul_eq_zero_iff (a b : mynat): a * b = 0 ↔ a = 0 ∨ b = 0 :=
data.editorText:
split,
  intro hab,
  apply eq_zero_or_eq_zero_of_mul_eq_zero,
  exact hab,
  intro hor,
  cases hor with ha hb,
    rw ha,
    rwa zero_mul,
    rw hb,
    rwa mul_zero,

data.lean: theorem mul_left_cancel (a b c : mynat) (ha : a ≠ 0) : a * b = a * c → b = c :=
data.editorText:
induction c with c hc generalizing b,
  rw mul_zero,
  intro hab,
  rw mul_eq_zero_iff at hab,
  cases hab with ha0 hb0,
  exfalso,
  apply ha,
  exact ha0,
  exact hb0,
  intro hab',
  cases b with b,
    rw mul_zero at hab',
    symmetry at hab',
    rw mul_eq_zero_iff a (succ c) at hab',
    cases hab' with ha0 hc0,
      exfalso,
      apply ha,
      exact ha0,
      symmetry at hc0,
      exact hc0,
    have hb := hc b,
    rw ← add_right_cancel_iff a (a * b) (a * c) at hb,
    repeat {rw mul_succ at hab'},
    have hbc := hb hab',
    rw ← succ_eq_succ_iff at hbc,
    exact hbc,
